        dc:description           "Figure 4. Ampharetidae and Melinnidae. Ampharetidae A Amage sp. nov. 1 B Anobothrus sp. nov. 1, anterior end methyl blue staining C Anobothrus sp. nov. 2 anterior end methyl blue staining. Melinnidae D Melinna cf. armandi and tube (AM W. 50354), d dorsal hook. Ampharetidae E Amphicteis sp. (AM W. 50429). Melinnidae F Melinnopsis gardelli anterior dorsal view (AM W. 50735) G Melinnopsis sp. nov., lateral view (AM W. 50397). Scale bars: 2 mm (A); 1 mm (B, C); 2.5 mm (D); 1 cm (E, G); 1 mm (F)." ;
